  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "The Amadeus H300 is a powerful Beam/Spot/Wash moving head with a powerful 300W bright white LED source and super smooth 3 phase motors. Equipped with 2 gobo wheels, 2 effect wheels and a rotating 3/8-facet prism to make stunning aerial effects in 8 colours plus white. The linear motorized zoom allows you to focus a beam up to 7° or open up to 32° to cover a wider area with ease. This true all-rounder can be controlled via RDM remote control, DMX, built-in automatic programs and presets, including a master/slave mode. Perfect for stage shows, productions, events, DJs, Bands, Venues, and more. A custom heavy-duty case is also available (option) to protect your fixtures during transport or storage.",
